<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM7.5">
<l>uṉṉō ṭuṭaṉē yorukaṭalil vāḻvārai</l>
<l>iṉṉā riṉaiyāreṉ ṟeṇṇuvā rillaikāṇ</l>
<l>maṉṉāki niṉṟa matucūtaṉ vāyamutam</l>
<l>paṉṉāḷu muṇkiṉṟāy pāñca caṉṉiyamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>See, there is no one to think of those who live with you in the same ocean</l>
<l>saying that [they are] such and such persons.</l>
<l>O Pāñcajanya! You have been eating every day the nectar that are the lips of</l>
<l>Madhusūdana, who is the Lord!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
